            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "歐洲央行總裁拉加德認為 川普若提高關稅對通膨影響甚微",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 歐洲央行行長克里斯蒂娜·拉加德表示，美國總統唐納德·川普再來一輪關稅對歐洲通膨的影響會極小。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">拉加德周三在接受RTL電台採訪時說道：「如果我們從短期來看，直接影響相對輕微。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據她說來，川普的最新威脅將使歐元區的平均關稅稅率從約12%，提高到15%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">她說：「通膨可能會受到非常輕微的影響，很可能是上升，但由於通膨率已控制在1.9%，因此影響將微乎其微。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">不過她警告說，包括德國在內的大型出口國將比其他國家遭受更大的打擊，並提醒人們注意可能出現的信心衝擊。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-032d9ad8-2435-3c1e-ab01-59c625c83450-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">拉加德說：「川普總統反覆無常所造成的不確定性，其影響要嚴重得多。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題ECB’s Lagarde Sees Little Impact on Inflation From More Tariffs</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C%E7%B8%BD%E8%A3%81%E6%8B%89%E5%8A%A0%E5%BE%B7%E8%AA%8D%E7%82%BA-%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E8%8B%A5%E6%8F%90%E9%AB%98%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85%E5%B0%8D%E9%80%9A%E8%86%A8%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E7%94%9A%E5%BE%AE-075910562.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-21 16:40:41",
